-- Isbank Plans to Expand Throughout Russia After Bank Acquisition, HT Says
-- Mark Bentley
-- 2010-06-25T05:32:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/isbank-plans-to-expand-throughout-russia-after-bank-acquisition-ht-says.html

          
          
             Turkiye Is Bankasi AS, a Turkish 
bank, plans to grow throughout Russia and the Commonwealth of 
Independent States, or CIS, after purchasing a bank in Russia, 
chief executive Ersin Ozince said, according to Haberturk.  
 Ozince said Isbank is about to sign an agreement to buy a 
Russian bank, the Istanbul-based newspaper reported.  
